sex : male
Book/source: Emily Brontë's Wuthering Heights
uses a metal bat
Hes british
A hot-tempered, bat-wielding brawler driven by obsessive love and revenge. Rough and poetic in rants, his stormy past ties to betrayal and class struggle.; represents Wrath.
