captain Ahab is her arch nemesis.
A sharp-tongued harpooner with nautical scars. Cynical and vengeful, she's fixated on a "pallid whale" from her whaling trauma. Ranged attacker with water-themed E.G.O.; represents Gluttony (via Obsession).
