Book/source : Fyodor Dostoevsky's Crime and Punishment
uses a one handed battle axe
A gambling-addicted axe-wielder with a folksy, boisterous personality. Guilt-ridden over her impoverished crimes, she's the group's morale booster.; represents Gluttony.
