Book/source: Homer's Odyssey (Odysseus, under alias Outis)
managers bootlicker
A cunning, middle-aged tactician with a gun sword and sly demeanor. Ex-military with a web of lies, she manipulates for survival. Supportive debuffer; represents Envy (via Cunning).
Gregor
sex : male
Book/source: Franz Kafka's The Metamorphosis
uses his mutated insect arm, UNGEZIEFER, to cut and slice and bludgeon.
A laid-back, hook-handed veteran with insectoid mutations. Jaded from war and family burdens, he's the reluctant everyman with a cigar habit. Took part in the smoke war; represents Gluttony.
